{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"ba6794069d","title":"给黄炎培的信","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"9a80034cb7","index":0,"year":1952,"month":6,"day":10,"articleId":"ba6794069d"}],"tags":[{"id":"2a70b5d939","name":"书信","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji32","name":"毛泽东全集第32卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives0/main/mao-quanji/32-OCR.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji32":{"comments":[{"id":"4053898ba4","publicationId":"maoquanji32","articleId":"ba6794069d","index":1,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"黄炎培，字任之，民主建国会主要负责人。当时任政务院副总理。"},{"id":"abc378734d","publicationId":"maoquanji32","articleId":"ba6794069d","index":2,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"林则徐，福建侯官（今福州）人。1840年鸦片战争时，任两广总督，是清朝官员中抵抗派的首领。"},{"id":"fb764af13b","publicationId":"maoquanji32","articleId":"ba6794069d","index":3,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"陈胜、吴广，是秦末农民起义的领袖。"}],"contents":[{"id":"f95407446c","type":"title","text":"给黄炎培的信","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji32","articleId":"ba6794069d"},{"id":"4053898ba4","type":"paragraph","text":"任之先生：","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji32","articleId":"ba6794069d"},{"id":"abc378734d","type":"paragraph","text":"六月八日惠书收到。一八四〇年是林则徐领导广州民众反抗英国进攻的那一年，即所谓鸦片战争的那一年，不是说陈胜吴广间，先生记错了。中国现代的革命，首先和最主要的目标是反对帝国主义的侵略，故可以上潮到反鸦片战争的林则徐及广州的“平英团”，上湖到二千余年前去纪念陈胜臭广，则太远了，那是古代的农民起义，不是现代的革命。此复。顺致敬意","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji32","articleId":"ba6794069d"},{"id":"fb764af13b","type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东","index":3,"publicationId":"maoquanji32","articleId":"ba6794069d"},{"id":"206961e73b","type":"paragraph","text":"六月十日","index":4,"publicationId":"maoquanji32","articleId":"ba6794069d"}],"page":{"id":"61ba9d12db","publicationId":"maoquanji32","articleId":"ba6794069d","start":133,"end":133}}}},"__N_SSG":true}